snippet.textDisplay:
Today (Sept 24th) is my birthday and I'm listening to this song on repeat. I frequently do it coz unfortunately its no longer available in spotify.
Out of all the chaap tilak covers ive heard.. This one is the best nd ethereal❤️.
I definitely cannot relate to the lyrics rn but the music and the vibe of this song makes me long for something that i never have... Its beyond words... Something i cannot describe properly.

And all those people who keep coming back to this song, this virtual hug is for you.🫂
I hope i find someone in real life too who lives this song like i do. 🕊️
